I can still hear him!

578
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:52,245
Play ball!

579
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:56,603
<i>And now the lineup
of the visiting Montreal Royals.</i>

580
00:41:56,760 --> 00:42:00,287
<i>Batting first, playing center field,
Marv Rackley.</i>

581
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:04,445
<i>Batting second, playing second base,
